yingyinNormal.zh: 但是你还有选择, 这个间办公室，这些员工, 年薪2200万美元都是你的。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, the alternative is no dialogue at all. We don't wanna leave any stone unturned. Sara.

yingyinNormal.en: That's thinking ahead. The alternative would be to think backwards. That's just remembering.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真会未雨绸缪。换句话说是怎么早没想到，这下记住了。

yingyinNormal.en: If you can't get Shao Hsing rice wine, then I would use dry sherry. That's a great alternative.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果没有绍兴米酒，你可以使用干雪利酒，也是个不错的替代品。

yingyinNormal.en: While the chicken's cooking, on to a great alternative to ham sandwiches, vegetable and ham wraps.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当鸡腿还在烤制时，我们再来做火腿三明治的绝佳替代品，蔬菜火腿卷。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, that's the point of an Oxford education. Isn't it, Dad? It's the expensive alternative to a dinner dance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不就是牛津教育的本质吗 爸爸? 不就是花大钱去舞会跳个舞吗?

yingyinNormal.en: I can see that. I was providing you with an alternative. A courtesy I was never offered in similar circumstances.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我看得出来，只是给你另外一个选择而已，而且是之前从未在类似情况下提供过的恩惠。

yingyinNormal.en: All right. What do you want? What is the goddamn alternative? Please, Claire, tell me, because I don't understand.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，你想要什么？你还有别的选择吗？求你了，克莱尔，我真的不懂。
